        <div class="row align-items-center justify-content-between">
            <div class="col-12 col-lg-5">
                <div class="about-content">
                    <h5>Who We Are</h5>
                    <p>We are what we think, and we think what we feed our minds with. Growing up as a 21st century
                        youth, I realized how much society is polluted with all sort of content to feed our minds.
                        Unconsciously, we tend to behave in ways that are influenced by all the polluted content out
                        there. This is a real problem because, content on the media, entertainment industry and wrong
                        norms and notions are becoming an integral part of us. Change begins from the mind. 
                        Under the guidance of the Holy Spirit, we aspire  to foster a movement of transformation
                        that will revitalise the minds of future generations and young people with Christ centred principles.
                        </p>
                   
                </div>



                    <div class="about-content">
                        <h5>Eagles Camp Meeting</h5>
