                        <h5>Coordinators Camp</h5>
                        <p>
                            This camp provides a unique opportunity for our hard-working 
                            coordinators to come together to share ideas,pray, and sharpen 
                            one another for the next level.
                        </p>
                    </div>


                    <div class="about-content">
                        <h5>Love Feasts</h5>
                        <p>
                            CGM organizes relationship seminars from time to time dubbed LOVE FEAST.
                            COVID-19 helped us to elevate the relationship seminar into an online monthly meeting with amazing participation
                            globally.
                        </p>
                    
                    </div>

                    <div class="about-content">
                        <h5>Mentoring HUB</h5>
                        <p>
                        In the monitoring HUB we devote time to provide mentoring to our young and upcoming executives.
                        </p>
                    
                    </div>
            </div>

